{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.cancel()","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><em><code>cancel()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>El método <code><strong>cancel()</strong></code> de la&nbsp;Web Animations API de la interfaz <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> borra todos los <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> causados por esta animación y aborta su reproducción.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>Cuando se cancela una animación, su <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\" title=\"startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a> y su <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\" title=\"currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a> se establecen en&nbsp; <code>null</code>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>Animation</em>.cancel();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parámetros","title":"Parámetros","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_devuelto","title":"Valor devuelto","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"excepciones","title":"Excepciones","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Este método no arroja excepciones directamente; sin embargo, si la animación <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\" title=\"playState\"><code>playState</code></a> no está <code>\"idle\"</code>\"inactiva\" cuando se cancela, el <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\" title=\"current finished promise\">current finished promise</a> se rechaza con un <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DomException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> llamado <code>AbortError</code>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-cancel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'Animation.cancel()' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Editor's draft.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.cancel","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>Animation.playState</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>Animation.finished</code></a> devuelve la promesa que esta acción rechazará si la animación de <code>playState</code> no está <code>\"idle\"</code> (\"inactiva\") .</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"El método cancel() de la Web Animations API de la interfaz Animation borra todos los KeyframeEffect (en-US) causados por esta animación y aborta su reproducción.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.cancel()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.cancel()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Animation.cancel()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Animation.cancel()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Animation.cancel()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/cancel","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/cancel/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel","title":"Animation.cancel()"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.cancel() - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}